Primary_Text: jə fydrɛ bɛ̃ĩ͉tuː gă̠rdɑː lĕ̞ biːtɛ͉

Alt_Transcription: yė fudrè bè̃ĩ̱tʋ̄ gărdā́ lĕ bītè̱

Primary_Text: ĭ fɔdrë d ă̠bɔ̆ wă̠rda̠ː ɛ̆ beːtɕə͉
